flowchart TB
    Start([Source Path]) --> Detect{Detect<br/>Format}
    
    Detect -->|Local File| LocalLoader[LocalFileLoader]
    Detect -->|dbfs:/| DBFSLoader[DBFSLoader]
    Detect -->|/Volumes/| UCLoader[Unity Catalog]
    Detect -->|https://| HTTPSLoader[HTTPSLoader]
    Detect -->|s3://| S3Loader[S3Loader]
    
    LocalLoader --> Archive{Compressed?}
    DBFSLoader --> Archive
    UCLoader --> Archive
    HTTPSLoader --> Archive
    S3Loader --> Archive
    
    Archive -->|.gz| Gunzip[Decompress gzip]
    Archive -->|.zip| Unzip[Extract zip]
    Archive -->|.tar.gz| Untar[Extract tar.gz]
    Archive -->|No| Stream
    
    Gunzip --> Stream[Stream Lines]
    Unzip --> Stream
    Untar --> Stream
    
    Stream --> ParseJSON{Valid<br/>JSON?}
    
    ParseJSON -->|Yes| EventType{Event<br/>Type}
    ParseJSON -->|No| ErrorLog[Log Error]
    
    EventType -->|JobStart| JobParser[Job Parser]
    EventType -->|StageSubmit| StageParser[Stage Parser]
    EventType -->|TaskStart| TaskParser[Task Parser]
    EventType -->|ExecutorAdded| ExecParser[Executor Parser]
    EventType -->|Other| OtherParser[Other Events]
    
    JobParser --> UpdateState[Update Internal State]
    StageParser --> UpdateState
    TaskParser --> UpdateState
    ExecParser --> UpdateState
    OtherParser --> UpdateState
    
    UpdateState --> Validate{Validate}
    Validate -->|Invalid| WarnLog[Log Warning]
    Validate -->|Valid| Continue
    
    WarnLog --> Continue{More<br/>Lines?}
    Continue -->|Yes| Stream
    Continue -->|No| Finalize[Finalize Models]
    
    Finalize --> BuildApp[Build SparkApplication]
    BuildApp --> End([Return Result])
    
    ErrorLog --> Continue
    
    style Start fill:#10b981,color:#fff
    style End fill:#10b981,color:#fff
